data.description: Investors/DYIs take note- this large home with loads of potential is located in the heart of Bridge City sitting on a 1 ACRE CORNER lot. Some improvements have been done to this spacious home which offers 3 beds, 3 baths, 2 fireplaces, a wood burning stove, hardwood floors, 2 living areas, 2 dining areas including a separate living suite all located close to shopping & restaurants. With a metal roof & ample storage, this great gem of a home is priced to sell & features so much that is worthy of the savvy buyer.
